CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1958, pg. 6 reads: "11. Grand prize winner Garvey Watson and family look over their prize, a Westinghouse Double-Oven Electric Range."
TitMainTitle: Grand prize winner Mr. and Mrs. Garvey Watson, shaking hands with unknown man, and family standing next to their new Westinghouse double-oven electric range at the 1958 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair in Syria Mosque
